association annual summer conference speaking by remote telephone 
hookup from the white house 
he pledged continued support for the education reform goals he 
and the governors agreed on last year and endorsed their revised 
plans for a national oversight panel that will grade the states and 
federal government on progress in meeting the goals democrats had 
insisted on the changes to deny republicans control of the panel 
i think it is essential there be some definitive way of 
