hampshire appeared before the governors sunday sununu said he 
couldnt talk about items that were a part of budget negotiations 
with congress 
but dukakis noted that the proposal wouldnt limit the deduction 
for local property taxes and that it just so happens new 
hampshire has the highest property taxes in the country new 
hampshire has no income tax 
