fraud involving the teamsters central pension fund and received a 
fiveyear federal prison term under a sentence commutation he 
received from president nixon in 1971 hoffa was barred from 
returning to office in the teamsters until 1980 
when hoffa vanished he was contesting that provision in court 
his son detroit attorney jimmy p hoffa has said he thinks his 
father was killed because he was trying to return to union power 
</TEXT>
