issuing a statement that gray was not a target of the investigation 
and was cooperating with the probe 
grays response rallied his supporters he not only survived but 
won the whips job handily over reps beryl anthony dark and 
david bonior dmich 
the whips job is that of chief votecounter and headknocker 
for the democratic leadership as it tries to pass legislation 
grays busy schedule of campaigning speechmaking and other 
