move democracy is tested he said 
move people were in lots of ways part of the 60s 
alienated turning away from the system reacting against excesses 
of big business corporations governments but this was 20 years 
later so what do you do with them well smash them murder 
them because there was no room for the option that they hold 
the story also concerns fathers and sons a topic of poignancy 
for wideman whose brother robert and son jacob are in prison 
